::Killfest/Scyther/Incarcinator::

"DarkFate was captured by an enemy faction," Killfest informs Scyther, "and we need to plan an attack against them. Right now we know very little about their base, so we need you to find out more. Can you do that?"

Scyther nods, looking over at Shivah. "DO you have any equipment more advanced than this scanner I'm sitting at?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Incarcinator looks at StarScream, feeling an ache in his head that he'd passed off as a battle wound. Now that his repair system was mostly done, though, he was feeling it more and more, since it wasn't being fixed at all.

"New battle? I havn't heard about it yet."
